---
import eq from "../assets/eq.jpg";
---

<section class="about-us">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="content">
      <h2 class="title">About us</h2>
      <p class="description">
        We are a leading supplier of axle and suspension solutions for the
        transportation industry in Poland. Year in and year out, we provide the
        highest quality components for truck fleets, building a reputation as a
        reliable partner in the logistics industry.
      </p>
      <p class="description">
        Nasza specjalizacja obejmuje kompleksowy asortyment części zamiennych
        oraz systemy zawieszeń dostosowane do wymagań współczesnych ciężarówek.
        Współpracujemy z wiodącymi europejskimi producentami, gwarantując
        produkty spełniające najwyższe standardy bezpieczeństwa i wydajności.
      </p>
      <p class="description">
        Our specialties include a comprehensive range of spare parts and
        suspension systems tailored to the requirements of modern trucks. We
        work with leading European manufacturers, guaranteeing products that
        meet the highest safety and performance standards.
      </p>
      <a href="#Email" class="cta-button">Contact us</a>
    </div>
    <div class="image-container">
      <img
        src={eq}
        alt="System zawieszenia ciężarówki"
        class="about-image"
        width="600"
        height="400"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-us {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background-color: #f8f9fa;

    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 4rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .content {
      .title {
        font-size: 2.9rem;
        color: red;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .description {
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: black;
        margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
      }

      .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
        background-color: red;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 0.375rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;

        &:hover {
          background-color: #c53030;
        }
      }
    }

    .image-container {
      position: relative;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);

      .about-image {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        object-fit: cover;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;

        &:hover {
          transform: scale(1.03);
        }
      }
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-us {
      .container {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 2rem;
      }

      .image-container {
        order: -1;
      }
    }
  }
</style>
